phase2.explanation:
🤖 **Common Repository mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| No caching | Add caching |
| No offline | Handle offline |
| No invalidation | Invalidate cache |
| Direct access | Use abstraction |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Add caching
private var cache: List<Player>? = null
private var lastFetch = 0L

// 2. Handle offline
try {
    return remote.getPlayers()
} catch (e: Exception) {
    return local.getPlayers()
}

// 3. Invalidate cache
fun invalidateCache() {
    cache = null
    lastFetch = 0L
}

// 4. Use abstraction
interface PlayerRepository
class PlayerRepositoryImpl : PlayerRepository
```

